ARTISAN IS LARAVEL'S COMMAND LINE INTERFACE WHICH MAKES DEVELOPMENT SMOOTHER

MIGRATION:- MIGRATIONS ARE VERSION CONTROL FOR YOUR DATABASE


facades in LARAVEL

facades provide us static interfaces to classes they provide a convenient way of using services without writing to use long class names

service providers in LARAVEL


SERVICE PROVIDERS BOOTSTRAPS ALL SERVICES IN OUR APPLICATIONS
INCLUDING CORE AND USER SERVICES


LARAVEL REQUEST LIFECYCLE

THE REQUEST FIRST ENTERS THE public/index.php file

it's passed to the HTTP KERNAL(BROWSER) OR CONSOLE KERNAL accordingly to whom request is for then it is passed to middleware after that routing determines the appropriate controller action to execute, controller logic is executed then repsonse is returned after that post response middleware is executed



SERVICE PROVIDERS IN LARAVEL

CERNTRAL CONFIGURATION POINT FOR LARAVEL APPLICATIONS
BOOTSTRAPS SERVCIES AND BINDS THEM TO SERVICE CONTAINER
REGISTER EVENT LISTENERS,MIDDLEWARES AND REOUTES


DEPENDENCY INJECTION AND SERVICE CONTAINERS

DEPENDENCY INJECTION provides external DEPENDENCY to objects

the service containsers manage class DEPENDENCYs and performs DEPENDENCY INJECTION


policy vs gate in LARAVEL

POLICY:- AUTHORIZATION LOGIC TIED TO A PARTICULAR MODEL
GATE:- GENERAL AUTHORIZATION LOGIC NOT TIED TO ANY MODEL


LARAVEL'S MACROS ALLOWS YOU TO ADD CUSTOM METHODS INTO YOUR BUILT IN CLASSES E.G COLLECCTION,repsonse AND REGISTER IN APPSERVICEPROVIDER.php

